definitions.definition: A village and civil parish in the Metropolitan Borough of Leeds , West Yorkshire , England ( OS grid ref SE2139 ) .
A former township in Hastings County , Ontario , Canada , now included in Stirling-Rawdon township.
A municipality in Matawinie Regional County Municipality, Lanaudière region, Quebec , Canada .
